data.description: Great value in this popular established neighborhood! This roomy brick ranch has been updated/upgraded to include:  NEWER the heat/air with Carrier unit, replacement windows, remodeled baths, Newer kitchen cabinets, counter tops, stainless appliances and tile floor! Converted garage has newer hardwood flooring and top of the line attic pull down. Low maintenance exterior with vinyl wrapped trim. Super-sized fenced back yard with oversize shed - room to build a detached garage if desired and above ground pool! Saratoga is located near airport, Norfolk base, Little Creek, and Botanical Gardens and major shopping. Converted family room 17 x 12. Hardwood floors in main living areas and bedrooms! Quiet street, convenient to shopping dining, beaches, bases!
